### PR Checklist

- Build: CMake config OK; project builds on CI; no compiler warnings.
- Style: naming matches rules; functions/classes are small; no god objects.
- Architecture: use cases isolated; no UI logic in application/domain; repositories only in infrastructure.
- Types: strong typing; no loose `void*`/C-style casts; headers are minimal.
- Tests: unit tests for domain/use cases updated and passing.
- UI: consistent theme, responsive layout, accessible controls.
